---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---
<SiteLayout title="Affiliate and Advertising Disclosure" description="How EmbroideryCalc labels affiliate links, sponsorships, advertising, product recommendations, and commercial relationships." canonicalPath="/affiliate-disclosure/">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-14 sm:px-6 sm:py-20">
    <p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-indigo-600">Commercial transparency</p>
    <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-black tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">Affiliate and advertising disclosure</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-bold text-slate-500">Last updated July 21, 2026</p>
    <div class="article-body mt-9">
      <p>EmbroideryCalc may earn money from clearly identified affiliate links, sponsored placements, or advertising. If you buy something through an eligible affiliate link, the seller may pay EmbroideryCalc a commission without changing your price.</p>
      <h2>How recommendations are selected</h2>
      <p>Relevance to the page or production context comes first. A backing article might contain a backing or hooping recommendation; a thread-matching tool might link to shade cards or thread. Commercial payout does not change calculator formulas, DST analysis, color-distance rankings, or editorial conclusions.</p>
      <h2>How commercial content is labeled</h2>
      <p>Pages containing affiliate links will include a disclosure near the content. Sponsored placements will use labels such as “Sponsored” or “Advertisement.” Ordinary source links and non-compensated manufacturer references will not be described as endorsements.</p>
      <h2>No guarantee</h2>
      <p>A linked product may not be suitable for every machine, design, garment, or shop. Confirm specifications, compatibility, price, availability, shipping, return policy, and safety information with the seller or manufacturer.</p>
      <h2>Current status</h2>
      <p>The site architecture reserves restrained, contextual positions for future partners, but this release does not ship a live affiliate catalog or advertising network. A placement stays hidden until a relationship and destination link have been reviewed.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
